title: NFC 'Freak Out' Scenarios
itunes:title: NFC 'Freak Out' Scenarios
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler – analyze the latest news from around the league including the Titans decision to cut Zach Mettenberger and Tom Coughlin's itch to coach again. The guys then decide if it is time for certain teams to freak out about possible personnel issues. Can the Seahawks overcome yet another weak offensive line? Should the Cowboys freak out when they look at their starting front seven?
